data.description: The right home at the right price!  This STEPLESS corner unit is in a prime location across from the Swim/Tennis/Cabana & Grills!  The 2 bedrooms and 2 baths are located at opposite ends of the home so this makes for the perfect Roommate Floorplan.  Updates include laminate floors, new carpet, new interior paint, new water heater, updated AC & more.  Just a short walk across the parking area and you can be cooking on the grills at the cabana or relaxing in one of the two pools.  If tennis is your game, this community has got you covered with 2 lighted courts - pickle ball too!  There are restaurants, shopping, and entertainment nearby.  A short drive to downtown Peachtree Corners, Historic Downtown Norcross, the Forum, Tech Park, St. Joe's, Merer, Oglethorpe and more.  Avoid interstate traffic with many options to enter/exit the area - Peachtree Industrial Blvd, Jimmy Carter, Holcomb Bridge, Peachtree Parkway, Spalding Dr, Buford Hwy and others.  Hurry, these sell fast, and this is a great price.
